Classes in it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.terms used by it.apice.sapere.api
AnnotatedVarTerm
           This interface models a logic-like annotated variable term for an Ecolaw.
Formula
           This interface models a boolean condition for annotated variables.
ListTerm
           This interface models a List of values inside an Ecolaw.
PatternNameTerm
           This interface models a PatternName inside an Ecolaw, which is a variable that represents an LSA-id for a matching LSA.
PropertyTerm
           This interface models a Property inside an Ecolaw.
SDescTerm
           This interface models a SemanticDescription that can be cloned or extended inside an Ecolaw.
ValueTerm
           This interface models a Value inside an Ecolaw.
VarTerm
           This interface models a logic-like unconstrained variable term for an Ecolaw.
